{"tid":1516402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過用老麥急口令快樂撚狗?","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:21:07.000Z","uid":306193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"787097cc4a4a2702152761f18ada9d1f50eb42f9","tid":1516402,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"好多時舖頭杯葛黑警都係話唔做佢哋生意﹐但係佢哋唔話畀你知就會冇咩作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要全天候欺凌黑警全家﹐就要搵更多人參與﹐最好令顧客都可以join埋<br />\n<br />\n例如學以前老麥啲急口令﹐限時內講到「香港警察正人渣﹐冚家剷泥死全家」之類嘅嘢﹐凍飲就唔使加兩蚊<br />\n<br />\n真係多人玩嘅話﹐分分鐘會connect到啲貪小便宜嘅中立顧客一齊講埋一份<br />\n<br />\n講咗急口令有著數攞﹐仲低成本過撳錢換美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33fd294379561fade0aa3702ffec2e146acc1c1","tid":1516402,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:25:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffe4a168443ecbcdda52131b49824f08895a9cf3","tid":1516402,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:33:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8764e23f6d0099274692fa828be1a8b5f53c87d9","tid":1516402,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c8166fe507f224f752ca7ce99a187f33bd41d61","tid":1516402,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f40efb49db6c532b07659c172348b29d8fe3390","tid":1516402,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d5b736001c7a757e9f321d9f64a5239a26bcdcf","tid":1516402,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:03:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df6f4ee3d83ead1c39f1b5dc8f816b3d46ddd5a5","tid":1516402,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}